{"tid":782431,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"介唔介意另一伴keep住前度既禮物","createTime":"2018-08-16T17:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T19:44:59.000Z","uid":201168,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c876516fc91f5f39c634df262615c4d19e7169e4","tid":782431,"uid":201168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:20:57.000Z","msg":"雖然另一伴話已經對前度無感覺<br />\n但仲keep住前度送d禮物<br />\n咁做令我硬係覺得有留戀<br />\n做人應該灑脫d<br />\n好介意但唔知點開口"},{"pid":"383d08b38e2331570181fed75aa455ed2788a793","tid":782431,"uid":169992,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:30:02.000Z","msg":"口講灑脫，自己又做唔到<br />\n最小器果個其實係你"},{"pid":"f4f0918539ce94195b95ed978fd537ae1a224cfc","tid":782431,"uid":165738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:30:24.000Z","msg":"直接、心平氣和咁講出你嘅感受啦樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔講谷住谷住仲辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e47899a757791ecabc123ce60dd72f9a713048","tid":782431,"uid":5921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:33:03.000Z","msg":"介意一定有既<br />\n但其實真係只係自己小氣<br />\n可能根本無留戀無所謂 純粹個樣野靚 做下裝飾"},{"pid":"dc6f73332560a01b6a48578fead76dfb9ef6d00f","tid":782431,"uid":2220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:38:07.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意就直接同佢講 介意前度係冇問題"},{"pid":"8fe90df50de92c4afc5972142ceeeafd8b3dfe43","tid":782431,"uid":158635,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:49:33.000Z","msg":"假設你個ex同你分手就可以即刻掉曬同你有關既野/忘記全部事<br />\n你會唔會覺得佢絕情先？又或者覺得ok好正常？<br />\n如果覺得唔正常既咪出聲話你介意囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我都好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da63eac9cebd2f5f0829e5fc9b5acb57ddf56d3","tid":782431,"uid":182317,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T21:51:37.000Z","msg":"好撚介意<br />\n話冇用但一直都唔掉<br />\n同佢講介意 就掉啲唔掉啲<br />\n即係點先 